-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-hamlet " href="/tags/hamlet">Hamlet</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-dublin " href="/tags/dublin">Dublin</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-oxford " href="/tags/oxford">Oxford</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-paris " href="/tags/paris">Paris</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-asia " href="/tags/asia">Asia</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-europe " href="/tags/europe">Europe</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-delphi " href="/tags/delphi">Delphi</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-algeria " href="/tags/algeria">Algeria</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-canada " href="/tags/canada">Canada</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-ethiopia " href="/tags/ethiopia">Ethiopia</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-greece " href="/tags/greece">Greece</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-agora " href="/tags/agora">Agora</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-house-of-lords " href="/tags/house-of-lords">House Of Lords</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-house-of-commons " href="/tags/house-of-commons">House Of Commons</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-university-of-london " href="/tags/university-of-london">University Of London</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-albin-lesky " href="/tags/albin-lesky">Albin Lesky</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-andrew-lang " href="/tags/andrew-lang">Andrew Lang</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-bruno-snell " href="/tags/bruno-snell">Bruno Snell</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-emerson " href="/tags/emerson">Emerson</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-dean-swift " href="/tags/dean-swift">Dean Swift</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-emile-zola " href="/tags/emile-zola">Emile Zola</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-demeter " href="/tags/demeter">Demeter</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-james-frazer " href="/tags/james-frazer">James Frazer</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-frank-turner " href="/tags/frank-turner">Frank Turner</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-hecuba " href="/tags/hecuba">Hecuba</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-george-grote " href="/tags/george-grote">George Grote</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-homeric " href="/tags/homeric">Homeric</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-jane-harrison " href="/tags/jane-harrison">Jane Harrison</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-jean-pierre-vernant " href="/tags/jean-pierre-vernant">Jean-Pierre Vernant</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-joseph-lafitau " href="/tags/joseph-lafitau">Joseph Lafitau</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-jowett " href="/tags/jowett">Jowett</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-karl-meuli " href="/tags/karl-meuli">Karl Meuli</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-laertes " href="/tags/laertes">Laertes</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-levi-strauss " href="/tags/levi-strauss">Levi Strauss</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-louis-gernet " href="/tags/louis-gernet">Louis Gernet</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-louis-macneice " href="/tags/louis-macneice">Louis MacNeice</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-macbeth " href="/tags/macbeth">Macbeth</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-marcel-detienne " href="/tags/marcel-detienne">Marcel Detienne</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-mark-twain " href="/tags/mark-twain">Mark Twain</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-moses-finley " href="/tags/moses-finley">Moses Finley</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-norman-mailer " href="/tags/norman-mailer">Norman Mailer</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-medea " href="/tags/medea">Medea</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-pierre-vidal-naquet " href="/tags/pierre-vidal-naquet">Pierre Vidal-Naquet</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-thomas-mann " href="/tags/thomas-mann">Thomas Mann</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-voltaire " href="/tags/voltaire">Voltaire</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-seamus-heaney " href="/tags/seamus-heaney">Seamus Heaney</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-walter-burkert " href="/tags/walter-burkert">Walter Burkert</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-black-sea " href="/tags/black-sea">Black Sea</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-william-ewart-gladstone " href="/tags/william-ewart-gladstone">William Ewart Gladstone</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-mediterranean " href="/tags/mediterranean">Mediterranean</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-british-columbia " href="/tags/british-columbia">British Columbia</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-ode-on-a-grecian-urn " href="/tags/ode-on-a-grecian-urn">Ode On A Grecian Urn</a><span class="tag-list-comma"></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></article></main><div class="ContainerPlacement OutBrain Engage-Wrapper"><div class="ContainerSection OutBrain Engage"><div class="OB-REACT-WRAPPER"><div class="OUTBRAIN" data-src="https://newrepublic.com/article/77364/the-oldest-dead-white-european-males"></div></div></div></div><div class="ad-unit ad-house_donate "><div class="htlad-House_DONATE"></div></div><footer class="footer fade-in " id="footer"><div class="footer__topRow"><ul class="footer__verticals